    "patch_code": "public static long get Octal( final String str ){\n\tlong result = 0;\n\tif (!str.isEmpty()) {\n\t\tStringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();\n\t\t\n\t\t// remove leading spaces\n\t while (sb.length < str.length && str.charAt( sb.length ) == ' ' ) {\n\t\t sb.append('0');\n\t}\n\t\t\n\t// remove trailing NULs or spaces\nwhile ( sb.length > 0 && (sb.charAt( sb.length - 1 ) == '0' || sb.charAt( sb.length - 1 ) == ' ')) {\n\t sb.set length - 1;\n\t}\n\t\t\n\t// convert from Octal\n\t for (int i = 0; i < sb.length; i++) {\n\t result *= 8;\n\t result +=  ( sb.charAt( i ) - '0');\n\t}\n\t}\n\treturn result;\n}",
